<HEAD>Missing Pig Found In Abandoned Movie Theater</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CALUMET CITY, Ill. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A 900-pound pet pig has been found
safe in an abandoned drive-in movie theater _ four days after
distraught owners reported a pignapping.
   Tiffany Marie's owner, Bob Urbanski, said he received an
anonymous phone call late Thursday threatening to harm the pig
unless it was retrieved on the theater grounds.
