   ``She looks fine,'' he said. ``She's eating grass and is content
as heck.''
   The 2-year-old spotted sow _ who likes corn chips and strawberry
whipped cream pie _ apparently was taken Sunday from an unfenced
yard behind Urbanksi family-run pet store in this suburb south of
Chicago.
